Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:18.32,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Your tear change real my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:27.36,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}流れる大気から 世界を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:32.46,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}タイムリミットは もう近いよ どうする?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:37.22,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Shout! 深い漆黒の眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:42.50,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Ah 消えない遺恨を背負うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:47.73,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はばたく闇の勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:50.13,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}掻き立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.52,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.70,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Strong my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:55.40,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}支配されても突き刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.94,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}賞賛は報酬で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.87,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}火照る美学鳴らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:06.65,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}涙は見せないで 今はまだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:10.79,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}譲ると誓うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:16.33,jpop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}解き放て REALIZE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:12.89,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}我啊… 将会改变整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:18.32,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}你的泪水牵动了我真实的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:27.36,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}于澎湃大气之中 震撼着世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:32.46,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}时限就快到了 该如何是好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:37.22,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}呼喊吧! 深邃的乌黑之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:42.50,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}啊 背负着无法消去的遗恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:47.73,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}大显身手的黑暗勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:50.13,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}崛地而起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.52,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.70,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}强化心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:55.40,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}就算遭到支配也要全力一击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.94,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}以赞赏作为报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.87,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}响起那令人热血的美学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:06.65,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}现在还不是让我看到你的泪水之时…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:10.79,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}我发誓会守护着你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:16.33,cnop,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}{\an8}不顾一切地来实现
Comment: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:38.34,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}愛のせいで眠れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:43.71,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そっぽ向いて眠れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:49.41,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}どんな風に始まるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:55.45,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}なんで声がかすれるのさ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:21:01.54,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}とまらない 胸騒ぎのdream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:06.52,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}囓った指が熱い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:15.45,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷うよ、怖いよ、駄目だよ…スキダヨ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:18.09,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}my story あるstory
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:26.75,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}お伽噺で寝かしつけるほど子どもじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:29.68,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}my story あるstory
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:40.12,jped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}キミのことだけ 考える日々じゃ苦しくなりそう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:38.34,cned,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}因为爱的缘故我睡不着觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:43.71,cned,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}因为视若无睹我睡不着觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:49.41,cned,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}会以怎样的形式开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:55.45,cned,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}为什么我的声音会哑口无言呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:21:01.54,cned,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}无法停下来 胸口中翻滚的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:06.52,cned,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}咬伤的指尖如此火热
